Mom, Dad.

18
00:02:58,439 --> 00:02:59,520
- You're here. - Shi Yi.

19
00:02:59,759 --> 00:03:01,479
I was worried you wouldn't be able to come alone.

20
00:03:01,599 --> 00:03:02,759
I have to come.

21
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,280
I got a birthday cake for you.

22
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,879
It's your favorite fruit cake.

23
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,479
That's great.

24
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:11,039
My daughter is the best.

25
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,400
Thank you.

26
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:15,280
It has been a while since our family got together.

27
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:17,800
You bought me clothes and dinner.

28
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,840
You shouldn't have.

29
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:21,080
Don't mention it. It's just dinner.

30
